findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward(), _getCurrentSupply, and bulkAntiBot() use loops that can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Potential OUT_OF_GAS exception in includeInReward() function
findings.description: The function includeInReward() uses a loop to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list, which may cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Potential OUT_OF_GAS exception in _getCurrentSupply function
findings.description: The function _getCurrentSupply uses a loop to evaluate total supply and could be aborted with an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Potential OUT_OF_GAS exception in bulkAntiBot() function
findings.description: The function bulkAntiBot() uses a loop to mark addresses as bots and could be aborted with an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long addresses list.
